{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>The Friendly Droppets</i></strong><i>\u00a0</i>is a simple physics based puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Droppets_Controls.png?t=1736180500\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Droppets_Controls.gif?t=1736180500\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take your time.<br>Rotate and position the <strong>Droppet</strong> and let it fall on the <strong>Panda</strong>'s head.<br>Try to collect the special item in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fill the gauge to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Droppets_Meter.gif?t=1736180500\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Droppets_Features.png?t=1736180500\" /> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pile and organize <strong>Droppets</strong> in 120 Levels;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience 12 Worlds with increasingly challenging <strong>Panda</strong> hats and movements<br>(you can play\u00a0<strong>the first 10 worlds, </strong>they are unlocked at the start on the Level Select screen);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect 15 types of object;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play the way you want (open the Option Screen on the main menu):</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Droppets_difficultyEasy.png?t=1736180500\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CASUAL</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For a relaxed gameplay;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slower <strong>Panda</strong> movements;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easier to fill gauge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Droppets_difficultyHard.png?t=1736180500\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CHALLENGE</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For more experienced players;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Faster <strong>Panda</strong> movements;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The gauge requires more <strong>Droppets</strong> to fill;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A counter appears on the bottom right corner (no incidence on the game play).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/Tips.png?t=1736180500\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can rotate the <strong>Droppet</strong> freely or by 45 degrees increments.<br>The closer the <strong>Droppet</strong>'s angle is to its landing surface's angle,<br>the less of a bounce will follow its landing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Placing too many <strong>Droppets</strong> directly on top of a single one<br>can push that <strong>Droppet</strong> out of the pile.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>Panda</strong> in the first levels of each world has no hat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to collect the object 3 times on <strong>Casual</strong> mode and only once in <strong>Challenge</strong> mode<br>to add it to your collection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fill a collection page to unlock an <strong>Achievement</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Take your time.</strong></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Stylistic Choice","path":"http